dc_description_s: This data layer represents parcels for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, “Rock_Parcels_2014.gdb”. [Created to assist Assessors in value determinations of Real Property in Rock County. Sources include, Certified Survey Maps, Subdivision Plats, Condominium Plats, Plats of Survey and Deeds recorded in the Register of Deeds Office. Drawing techniques include COGO and heads up digitizing from Aerial Photography. Parcels are depicted using the most current information available.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
